msgid "Sout stream"
msgstr "бһҹбҹ’бһ‘бҹ’бһҡбһёбһҳ Sout"

#: include/vlc_config_cat.h:163
msgid ""
"Sout stream modules allow to build a sout processing chain. Please refer to "
